outputs.output_descr:
. Green House Gas emission baseline assessment on priority sectors conducted, climate resilient green economy investment plan prepared and action learning early activities implemented, 
2. Climate Resilient Green Economy (CRGE) strategy   mainstreamed into the national and sub-national development planning, cooperation, budgeting and Monitoring and evaluation 
3. Ethiopian national Climate Resilient Green Economy financing mechanism - CRGE facility established and operationalized 
4.   Climate Resilient Green Economy planning, coordination and implementation capacity at the Ministry of Agriculture enhanced 
5. Climate Resilient Green Economy implementation capacity at the federal Ministry Of Water and Energy enhanced and energy policy reviewed;
6.  Climate Resilient Green Economy implementation capacity at the federal Ministry Of Industry enhanced;
